        <ul class="text-sm text-ink-soft mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="arrow">→</span> 1 dev senior full-stack (4 meses)</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="arrow">→</span> 1 IA engineer (2 meses parcial)</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="arrow">→</span> 1 diseñador UX/UI (5 semanas)</li>
